{"id": 2143, "genre": 1000, "title": "当人们讨论受害者时，都有哪些跑偏?", "description": "这样的荒诞一直存在：比起谴责犯罪者，人们对受害者的攻击和伤害从没停止过。", "record_count": 9998, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201801251123462QyrcZqTOf1viWAJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-28T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3641, "title": "当人们讨论受害者时，都有哪些跑偏?", "content": "当人们讨论受害者时，都有哪些跑偏？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 261703, "content": "受害者有道德瑕疵就是活该，“有黑历史不值得同情”", "image": "img/option/option/20180125113106HhzgLDIB4blY7CWZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261709, "content": "不从加害者而从受害者身上找原因，“被骚扰是因为穿太暴露”", "image": "img/option/option/20180125114212AsFWZThIciSBdQa2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261716, "content": "用受害者的反应来归责，“这么冷静一点都不像被害”", "image": "img/option/option/201801251145423UPx08yIjRwO4iAl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261717, "content": "把受害者跟事件长期捆绑，正常生活也被过度解读", "image": "img/option/option/20180125114649ROWChHIiUcmSyg2s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261719, "content": "要求受害者条理清晰逻辑严密证据确凿，“漏洞太多一看就是假的”", "image": "img/option/option/20180125114906uZozX9KLQBGA4Urf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261720, "content": "一旦涉及到赔偿就把受害者诉求全归结为“都是为了钱”", "image": "img/option/option/20180125115005KtFRdyiOEPSvjX0N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261722, "content": "默认弱势有理，“强势一方怎么会被害”", "image": "img/option/option/201801251151164ga5vD9CiOzpTRZc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261713, "content": "受害者本人也自我审查，“这事我也有错，就算了吧”", "image": "img/option/option/20180125114355QR8swPjm3eT6iNXn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}